Eligius,is,a,Bitcoin,mining,operation,named,for,Saint,Eligius,the,patron,saint,of,goldsmiths,metalworkers,and,coin,collectors,The,Eligius,mining,pool,has,no,fees,and,no,registration,is,required,The,operation,exposes,information,about,its,pool,and,miners,through,its,stats,page,and,its,API,The,Eligius,API,allows,users,to,retrieve,data,on,pool,miners,earnings,and,balances,the,amount,of,shares,available,payouts,and,user,output,via,REST,calls